हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: When Hazel walks back into Liam’s life, she’s a stranger to him—but he’s still her everything. As pieces of the past start to return, so do the feelings. Say You Remember, Say You Love is a bittersweet tale of amnesia, forgiveness, and the fight to reclaim a forgotten love.

Say You Remember, Say You Love is a bittersweet tale of amnesia, forgiveness, and the fight to reclaim a forgotten love.
